The paper focuses on improving change prediction models in software engineering by using code smell-related information. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also involves metrics and evaluation of models, which could fall under cs.PL (Programming Languages) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the negative impact of code smells, which could be related to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SD (Software Development).
